Class GridDefinition

  • java.lang.Object
    • com.jasonwjones.pbcs.api.v3.dataslices.GridDefinition

  • public class GridDefinition
extends Object
    POJO used to model grid for Export Data Slice operation on PBCS REST API. Should be kept as clean as possible (i.e. avoid temptation to add convenience methods).
    Author:
    jasonwjones

      • setColumns

        public void setColumns(List<DimensionMembers> columns)
        Columns are modeled... kind of fucking stupidly. Think of it as a single array for all of the columns, one element per column. The object in that array is one or more strings that extend down the sheet.
        Parameters:
        columns - the column definition
